or questioned.

42:04.994 --> 42:06.796
They rarely come up
in open court.

42:06.831 --> 42:08.391
Law schools don't teach them.

42:08.426 --> 42:10.635
Also, the attorneys
who represent the victims

42:10.670 --> 42:12.934
can get up to 40%
of the settlement.

42:12.969 --> 42:15.035
