a confidentiality clause.

42:20.405 --> 42:22.680
And the women who sign these
contracts have to give over

42:22.715 --> 42:25.947
all of their evidence:
their diaries, emails, phones.

42:25.982 --> 42:27.377
It's cash for silence,

42:27.412 --> 42:29.445
