if you're a freelancer

42:55.077 --> 42:57.242
or if there are fewer than
15 employees in the workplace.

42:57.277 --> 42:59.145
Also, most lawyers
prefer settlements

42:59.180 --> 43:01.752
'cause it's less of
a financial risk for them.

43:01.787 --> 43:03.413
How close are
any of these actresses

43:03.448 --> 43:04.612
