49:46.851 --> 49:49.753
Harvey had this--
what did they call it?--

49:49.788 --> 49:55.396
"a physical altercation" with a
male employee at a conference.

49:55.431 --> 49:57.024
Then they settled with the guy.

49:57.059 --> 49:59.268
And with women?

50:00.667 --> 50:02.634
He pursued them.

50:02.669 --> 50:04.399
Endlessly.

50:07.476 --> 50:09.674
What happened in Venice?

50:11.612 --> 50:13.579
I don't want to be quoted.

50:13.614 --> 50:14.382
Period.

50:14.417 --> 50:16.549
Understood.

50:20.489 --> 50:21.983
We were in Harvey's suite,

50:22.018 --> 50:24.821
and (sniffles) there were
a bunch of people in there.

50:24.856 --> 50:27.395
And there were
these two assistants,

50:27.430 --> 50:30.266
and they were
sitting there trembling.

50:30.301 --> 50:32.059
And Weinstein was there?

50:32.094 --> 50:34.204
Yes.

50:34.239 --> 50:37.669
He was talking film
and ignoring them,

50:37.704 --> 50:40.606
but they were
literally vibrating.

50:40.641 --> 50:44.280
One with fear,
the other with anger.

50:46.515 --> 50:48.284
Can you tell me their names?

50:48.319 --> 50:50.319
Yes.

50:55.161 --> 50:59.020
And there's another woman
you should, you should call.

50:59.055 --> 51:02.562
The two assistants are
Rowena Chiu and Zelda Perkins,

51:02.597 --> 51:05.697
and we have a third name,
Laura Madden.

51:05.732 --> 51:08.436
And none of them
are returning our calls.

51:08.471 --> 51:10.339
So? Show up in person.

51:10.374 --> 51:12.737
Yeah. (chuckles)

51:12.772 --> 51:17.104
They live in London,
Silicon Valley and Wales.

51:17.139 --> 51:19.414
Can you get on a plane?

51:21.814 --> 51:23.946
(laughs)

51:26.258 --> 51:29.490
Let me work it out with Ron.

51:32.264 --> 51:35.265
But yeah, of course.

51:35.300 --> 51:36.860
Documents, verification.

51:36.895 --> 51:38.334
You know what we need.

51:38.369 --> 51:40.600
♪ ♪

