52:16.407 --> 52:18.638
(dog barking in distance)

52:22.006 --> 52:24.105
JODI:
Hi.

52:24.140 --> 52:26.745
Sorry to bother you.
I can see you're busy.

52:26.780 --> 52:30.287
I was looking for Rowena Chiu.

52:30.322 --> 52:31.816
Hi.

52:31.851 --> 52:35.116
Rowena's not here right now.
Can I give her a message?

52:35.151 --> 52:37.019
When will she be back?

52:37.054 --> 52:40.088
My wife's out of the country
for a while.

52:40.123 --> 52:41.397
(chuckles) I see.

52:41.432 --> 52:44.125
I did try calling her.

52:44.160 --> 52:45.533
This a work thing?

52:45.568 --> 52:47.502
No. You must be Andrew?

52:47.537 --> 52:48.998
Andrew Cheung?

52:49.033 --> 52:51.803
I'm Jodi Kantor.
I'm from<i> The New York Times.</i>

52:51.838 --> 52:53.508
Okay.

52:53.543 --> 52:57.413
So, what did you want
to talk to Rowena about?

52:57.448 --> 53:00.581
We're researching a story
about Miramax.

53:00.616 --> 53:03.485
I flew in from New York.

53:03.520 --> 53:05.850
-You came all this way?
-Yeah.

53:05.885 --> 53:07.258
(Andrew chuckles)

53:07.293 --> 53:09.887
Um, could we talk for a minute?

53:09.922 --> 53:11.394
Sure.

53:11.429 --> 53:14.463
So, I've been speaking
with people

53:14.498 --> 53:17.829
who worked for Harvey Weinstein.

53:17.864 --> 53:21.668
You're going quite far back
with Rowena's time there.

53:21.703 --> 53:23.703
We're writing about
his treatment of women.

53:23.738 --> 53:25.034
Right.

53:25.069 --> 53:28.169
And Rowena fits in how?

53:28.974 --> 53:32.382
Your wife worked at Miramax
for some years.

53:32.417 --> 53:34.615
Yes.

53:34.650 --> 53:35.946
Mainly in Hong Kong.

53:35.981 --> 53:37.750
Like to hear about
her experiences

53:37.785 --> 53:39.290
working for Weinstein.

53:39.325 --> 53:42.458
I'm confused why you can't
discuss it on the phone.

53:42.493 --> 53:44.955
(laughs) I did try.

53:44.990 --> 53:47.364
It is always better
to actually meet.

53:49.258 --> 53:50.994
So...

53:52.701 --> 53:55.834
And this is off the record.

53:55.869 --> 53:57.935
My understanding is that...
(stammers)

53:57.970 --> 53:59.871
that Weinstein
possibly victimized your wife

53:59.906 --> 54:02.137
when Rowena
first worked for him.

54:05.582 --> 54:09.386
Rowena's never mentioned
anything like that to me.

54:09.421 --> 54:11.212
What-what do you mean
by "victimized"?

54:11.247 --> 54:12.719
Can you be more specific?

54:14.118 --> 54:15.623
I was told that your wife

54:15.658 --> 54:18.120
may have received a settlement
from Weinstein.

54:18.925 --> 54:22.399
(scoffs) Do I look like a guy
whose wife got a settlement?

54:23.732 --> 54:26.128
Could you have confused her
with someone else?

54:26.163 --> 54:29.197
I-I... I apologize
for taking up your time.

54:29.232 --> 54:30.572
I'm...

54:30.607 --> 54:33.872
Will you just please
give this to Rowena?

54:33.907 --> 54:35.412
If you're talking
to these other people,

54:35.447 --> 54:36.809
why do you need
to talk to Rowena?

54:36.844 --> 54:39.878
And if you turn up
in my driveway,

54:39.913 --> 54:41.616
what kind of victimization?

54:41.651 --> 54:43.354
It's complex.

54:43.389 --> 54:45.620
I'm asking you to expand on it.

54:45.655 --> 54:49.723
I really think
it would be best...

54:50.594 --> 54:52.495
...if you asked Rowena.

54:52.530 --> 54:54.497
Have a good day.

55:02.364 --> 55:04.001
(engine starts)

55:06.841 --> 55:08.973
JODI (over phone):
<i> I just couldn't lie to him.</i>

55:09.008 --> 55:11.481
And then it turns out
he didn't know.

55:11.516 --> 55:13.274
What if London is
a repeat of this?

55:13.309 --> 55:14.748
It won't be.

55:14.783 --> 55:16.981
I spoke with an
employment lawyer in the U.K.,

55:17.016 --> 55:20.589
and he told me that
it was irresponsible of me

55:20.624 --> 55:22.624
even to ask about
breaching NDAs.

55:22.659 --> 55:24.318
No one does it.
They would get sued.

55:24.353 --> 55:25.891
Fuck that guy.

55:25.926 --> 55:29.224
Honestly, Jodi, fuck him.
He has no idea.

55:29.259 --> 55:31.897
I wish I smoked or something.

55:31.932 --> 55:34.933
I'm staring at
an actual brick wall,

55:34.968 --> 55:37.232
and all I can think is, "Fuck."

55:37.267 --> 55:39.509
That's okay.

55:39.544 --> 55:41.137
Fuck.

55:41.172 --> 55:43.645
And documents.

55:47.618 --> 55:50.245
(woman speaking indistinctly
over P.A.)

55:52.920 --> 55:57.087
So, Laura, we are looking at
a full mastectomy.

55:57.122 --> 56:01.157
And we should schedule this
as soon as possible.

56:01.192 --> 56:02.796
I understand.

56:07.539 --> 56:09.770
(line ringing)

56:11.367 --> 56:12.872
LAURA (over phone):
Hello.

56:12.907 --> 56:15.006
Hi.

56:15.041 --> 56:17.712
Laura, this is Jodi Kantor
from<i> The New York Times.</i>

56:17.747 --> 56:20.341
Um, I hope you've been
getting my messages.

56:20.376 --> 56:21.782
I'm in California right now,

56:21.817 --> 56:24.213
but I'm coming
to London tomorrow.

56:24.248 --> 56:26.149
Hi, Jodi.

56:26.184 --> 56:27.414
Hi.

56:27.449 --> 56:31.594
Um, I-I'm so happy to be
finally speaking with you.

56:31.629 --> 56:34.762
I-I understand that you once
worked for Harvey Weinstein

56:34.797 --> 56:37.061
in the London office of Miramax.

56:37.096 --> 56:38.799
Is that right?

56:40.165 --> 56:42.363
Laura?

56:42.398 --> 56:44.805
(Laura crying)

56:48.173 --> 56:49.711
Laura.

56:49.746 --> 56:51.482
(sighs)

56:51.517 --> 56:53.583
Can I do anything to help?

56:53.618 --> 56:56.377
No. I can't talk
about this right now.

56:56.412 --> 56:57.851
(line clicks)

56:58.623 --> 57:00.854
♪ ♪

57:05.894 --> 57:07.927
(kids chattering quietly)

57:09.601 --> 57:11.425
Hey.

57:11.460 --> 57:12.668
Hey, my love.

57:12.703 --> 57:15.968
-Come here. Oh.
-(crying softly)

57:16.971 --> 57:18.938
Hey, now.

57:19.809 --> 57:22.139
It's going to be all right.

57:22.174 --> 57:24.812
-It's going to be all right.
-GRACIE: I'm so sorry, Mum.

57:24.847 --> 57:27.078
(crying and sniffling continues)

57:29.511 --> 57:31.753
