57:39.895 --> 57:41.565
WOMAN (over P.A.):
Please refrain from smoking

57:41.600 --> 57:43.424
in this building.

57:43.459 --> 57:45.701
(engines idling)

57:49.839 --> 57:52.840
(jet engine whirring
in distance)

57:55.812 --> 57:57.614
WAITRESS:
Here we are.

58:00.509 --> 58:02.212
Tea.

58:02.247 --> 58:04.049
Thank you.

58:17.097 --> 58:18.393
(sniffs)

58:22.201 --> 58:24.608
You know, other people
have tried to write this story.

58:24.643 --> 58:25.939
He kills it every time.

58:25.974 --> 58:28.205
We're aware of that.

58:29.109 --> 58:31.747
And we're not gonna
let that happen to us.

58:35.720 --> 58:37.346
Are you okay, Zelda?

58:37.381 --> 58:38.952
Yes.

58:41.088 --> 58:44.287
So, you started working
at Miramax when you were 21?

58:44.322 --> 58:48.060
Yes. I was an assistant
at the London office.

58:48.095 --> 58:50.326
-And how was it?
-It was great.

58:50.361 --> 58:53.263
But it would shift
when Harvey came to town.

58:53.298 --> 58:54.869
In what way?

58:54.904 --> 58:58.741
Everyone became on call
to Harvey.

58:58.776 --> 59:01.040
And what would that entail?

59:01.075 --> 59:06.441
Script meetings, discussions
and more personal stuff.

59:06.476 --> 59:07.915
Like?

59:07.950 --> 59:10.511
For instance,
I would have to go to his hotel

59:10.546 --> 59:12.656
and wake Harvey up.

59:12.691 --> 59:14.383
Run his shower for him.

59:14.418 --> 59:15.824
Get him out of bed.

59:15.859 --> 59:17.353
He would usually be naked.

59:17.388 --> 59:19.553
And he might try
to pull me onto him.

59:19.588 --> 59:21.291
What did you do?

59:21.326 --> 59:22.831
I'd fend him off.

59:22.866 --> 59:25.900
I found humor or aggression
worked best.

59:25.935 --> 59:29.772
Harvey was either
excited or furious.

59:29.807 --> 59:31.939
You never knew
which it would be.

59:32.711 --> 59:35.712
Did anyone on the team
give you advice about him?

59:35.747 --> 59:37.274
Yes. (chuckles)

59:37.309 --> 59:40.244
Once, one girl told me to
always wear my puffer jacket,

59:40.279 --> 59:43.115
um, and to always sit
in an armchair,

59:43.150 --> 59:47.284
never the sofa next to him,
which helped.

59:47.319 --> 59:51.794
And that's how I knew that
it wasn't only happening to me.

59:51.829 --> 59:53.829
What was happening exactly?

59:53.864 --> 59:55.666
Bullying.

59:55.701 --> 59:57.459
Emotional abuse.

59:57.494 --> 1:00:00.330
I was just too young
to understand it.

1:00:00.365 --> 1:00:03.707
Harvey wanted people
to submit to him.

1:00:03.742 --> 1:00:04.873
And if they didn't?

1:00:04.908 --> 1:00:06.369
Well, then he'd roar.

1:00:06.404 --> 1:00:07.843
And he'd spit.

1:00:07.878 --> 1:00:10.747
He could destroy someone
in seconds.

1:00:10.782 --> 1:00:13.013
Were you scared of him?

1:00:13.818 --> 1:00:16.753
Yes. We all were.

1:00:19.120 --> 1:00:21.153
So, three years into this,

1:00:21.188 --> 1:00:23.925
you were at
the Venice Film Festival.

1:00:26.622 --> 1:00:29.293
I resigned after that. (sniffs)

1:00:29.328 --> 1:00:32.560
-What happened?
-I can't tell you all of it.

1:00:32.595 --> 1:00:34.771
What can you tell me?

1:00:34.806 --> 1:00:37.235
♪ Let's sway ♪

1:00:37.270 --> 1:00:43.142
♪ Under the moonlight,
this serious moonlight... ♪

1:00:44.046 --> 1:00:45.749
ZELDA:
<i> There was a new assistant.</i>

1:00:45.784 --> 1:00:47.575
<i> She was my age. She was great.</i>

1:00:47.610 --> 1:00:48.719
(both chuckling)

1:00:48.754 --> 1:00:50.380
<i> She was very smart.</i>

1:00:50.415 --> 1:00:52.855
<i> And she was doing Harvey's</i>
<i> evening script meeting</i>

1:00:52.890 --> 1:00:54.450
<i> alone for the first time,</i>

1:00:54.485 --> 1:00:58.025
<i> and I told her to call me</i>
<i> if he got difficult.</i>

1:00:59.721 --> 1:01:01.523
-Was he pursuing her?
-No.

1:01:01.558 --> 1:01:03.063
(chuckles softly)

1:01:03.098 --> 1:01:06.462
Harvey said, "I don't like
Jewish or Asian women."

1:01:06.497 --> 1:01:08.332
-But that night...
-She called you.

1:01:08.367 --> 1:01:09.333
No.

1:01:09.368 --> 1:01:10.202
(knock on door)

1:01:10.237 --> 1:01:11.566
<i> The following morning,</i>

1:01:11.601 --> 1:01:14.943
<i> she came to me,</i>
<i> and she was sobbing.</i>

1:01:14.978 --> 1:01:16.747
<i> -I mean, she was hysterical.</i>
-(sobbing)

1:01:16.782 --> 1:01:18.408
Rowena, what happened?

1:01:18.443 --> 1:01:20.146
Sit.

1:01:20.181 --> 1:01:22.918
<i> -And I held her.</i>
-What is it?

1:01:23.712 --> 1:01:26.548
Did she tell you what he did?

1:01:27.826 --> 1:01:29.683
Not exactly.

1:01:29.718 --> 1:01:31.487
Only that no one must know.

1:01:31.522 --> 1:01:32.994
But I knew.

1:01:33.029 --> 1:01:35.260
I knew that he must've...

1:01:36.868 --> 1:01:38.098
What?

1:01:38.133 --> 1:01:40.100
She was so upset.

1:01:40.135 --> 1:01:44.434
I knew that it had to be
the-the worst possible thing.

1:01:45.470 --> 1:01:48.537
I calmed her down, and I went
straight to confront Harvey.

1:01:48.572 --> 1:01:51.639
He was in a meeting, uh,
with Scorsese, who, you know...

1:01:51.674 --> 1:01:54.785
who hated him, so it was
a really big deal for Harvey.

1:01:54.820 --> 1:01:58.514
And I went straight up to him,
and I said very clearly,

1:01:58.549 --> 1:02:00.252
"You need to come with me
right now."

1:02:00.287 --> 1:02:02.859
You went right up to them
and confronted him?

1:02:02.894 --> 1:02:05.092
Yeah. I was so angry.

1:02:05.127 --> 1:02:07.490
And in front of everyone,

1:02:07.525 --> 1:02:10.658
he stood up and...

1:02:10.693 --> 1:02:12.902
he followed me like a lamb.

1:02:14.037 --> 1:02:17.698
And then I knew.
Then I knew he did it.

1:02:17.733 --> 1:02:19.436
And then?

1:02:19.471 --> 1:02:20.668
He denied it.

1:02:20.703 --> 1:02:22.241
He said, "I swear on my wife
and kids' lives

1:02:22.276 --> 1:02:23.638
that I did not assault
that young woman."

1:02:23.673 --> 1:02:26.773
(chuckles) And then
I knew that he was lying.

1:02:26.808 --> 1:02:28.181
He always used that line

1:02:28.216 --> 1:02:30.447
as a "get out of jail free"
card. Always.

1:02:31.252 --> 1:02:34.891
Did the assistant
report it to the police?

1:02:34.926 --> 1:02:38.092
Mm. She told no one.

1:02:39.865 --> 1:02:41.755
We came back to London.

1:02:41.790 --> 1:02:42.998
We both resigned.

1:02:43.033 --> 1:02:44.527
I told my direct superior,

1:02:44.562 --> 1:02:48.872
who suggested
we get ourselves a good lawyer.

1:02:48.907 --> 1:02:50.599
I had no idea where to get one.

1:02:50.634 --> 1:02:52.601
I found a company
close to the office,

1:02:52.636 --> 1:02:55.142
and-and then I thought
it would be simple.

1:02:55.177 --> 1:02:56.440
Criminal proceedings.

1:02:56.475 --> 1:02:58.640
But our lawyer said
we had no chance

1:02:58.675 --> 1:03:00.851
and the only thing to do
was to agree to a settlement.

1:03:00.886 --> 1:03:02.215
And I said categorically no,

1:03:02.250 --> 1:03:03.953
that no money
should change hands

1:03:03.988 --> 1:03:05.383
and that we just wanted
to stop him.

1:03:05.418 --> 1:03:08.023
And no U.K. police
were involved?

1:03:08.058 --> 1:03:09.585
We had no case.

1:03:09.620 --> 1:03:11.785
We had no evidence and
no police report from Venice.

1:03:11.820 --> 1:03:13.292
And, you see, with rape,

1:03:13.327 --> 1:03:15.030
it is impossibly difficult
to get a prosecution.

1:03:15.065 --> 1:03:16.559
And the lawyers kept saying

1:03:16.594 --> 1:03:19.166
damage limitation
was the only way to go.

1:03:19.201 --> 1:03:21.399
So I said, "All right, then.

1:03:21.434 --> 1:03:23.104
We have our own
very real demands."

1:03:23.139 --> 1:03:25.040
Conditions that Harvey
would have to meet

1:03:25.075 --> 1:03:26.206
if we were to sign.

1:03:26.241 --> 1:03:27.768
And what were those conditions?

1:03:27.803 --> 1:03:30.342
We demanded that if Harvey
had another settlement

1:03:30.377 --> 1:03:32.707
within two years, that it had
to be reported to Disney

1:03:32.742 --> 1:03:34.082
or else he would be fired.

1:03:34.117 --> 1:03:36.777
Another was that
he would go to therapy,

1:03:36.812 --> 1:03:38.152
with me present initially

1:03:38.187 --> 1:03:40.154
so that he couldn't lie
to the therapist.

1:03:40.189 --> 1:03:42.959
We demanded that
HR would put in a system

1:03:42.994 --> 1:03:45.324
to protect the women and staff.

1:03:45.359 --> 1:03:48.195
And it felt like if we could
achieve all of those,

1:03:48.230 --> 1:03:50.197
then that's what our silence
was paying for,

1:03:50.232 --> 1:03:53.266
that we were paying
for him to stop.

1:03:55.039 --> 1:03:56.500
So we signed.

1:03:56.535 --> 1:03:59.635
And they had their own
insane conditions for us.

1:03:59.670 --> 1:04:01.307
What were they?

1:04:02.211 --> 1:04:03.672
I tried to commit them
to memory.

1:04:03.707 --> 1:04:05.674
Um, they wouldn't give us
our own copy.

1:04:05.709 --> 1:04:07.313
What?

1:04:07.348 --> 1:04:09.282
I was only given visitation
rights to my own settlement.

1:04:09.317 --> 1:04:11.779
That's in... (stammers)

1:04:11.814 --> 1:04:13.187
That's incredible.

1:04:13.222 --> 1:04:15.453
But you memorized them?

1:04:16.588 --> 1:04:22.262
I asked for letters, too, which
stated some of the conditions.

1:04:22.297 --> 1:04:25.826
One said,
"We will make best endeavors

1:04:25.861 --> 1:04:29.698
to not help the police
in a criminal or civil case."

1:04:29.733 --> 1:04:34.571
We weren't allowed to talk
to our family or a doctor.

1:04:36.377 --> 1:04:39.081
So finally we signed.

1:04:39.116 --> 1:04:41.908
They gave us some money.

1:04:41.943 --> 1:04:44.614
And I felt completely broken.

1:04:45.584 --> 1:04:47.617
♪ ♪

1:04:52.426 --> 1:04:54.129
<i> I interviewed</i>
<i> for other jobs afterwards,</i>

1:04:54.164 --> 1:04:57.297
<i> but everyone kept saying,</i>
<i> "Why did you leave Harvey?"</i>

1:05:03.107 --> 1:05:05.206
<i> They all assumed that I'd...</i>

1:05:06.044 --> 1:05:07.868
...been with him, you know.

1:05:07.903 --> 1:05:09.606
It was horrible.

1:05:11.874 --> 1:05:13.313
What did you do then?

1:05:13.348 --> 1:05:15.843
I went to visit a friend
in Guatemala,

1:05:15.878 --> 1:05:17.911
and I stayed for five years.
(chuckles)

