1:19:19.963 --> 1:19:23.162
Powerful men
of an older generation

1:19:23.197 --> 1:19:24.592
are changing their understanding

1:19:24.627 --> 1:19:26.561
of the meaning of the word
"consensual."

1:19:26.596 --> 1:19:28.530
Why women don't feel
it's consensual

1:19:28.565 --> 1:19:31.401
even if a man
convinces himself it is.

1:19:31.436 --> 1:19:34.008
Do you want to expand on that?

1:19:34.043 --> 1:19:36.604
Uh, I believe (chuckles)

1:19:36.639 --> 1:19:39.706
there's a story to be told
about the evolution of men.

1:19:39.741 --> 1:19:42.313
And, in particular, Harvey
on this subject.

1:19:42.348 --> 1:19:45.085
Uh, would he be willing
to talk to us about it?

1:19:45.120 --> 1:19:47.351
On the record.

1:19:48.288 --> 1:19:50.816
He has to deal with
his wife and children

1:19:50.851 --> 1:19:52.125
before anything else.

1:19:52.930 --> 1:19:58.395
You're adamant Rose McGowan's
rape accusation is false.

1:19:58.430 --> 1:20:00.199
Why is that?

1:20:00.234 --> 1:20:01.937
Did she tell anybody right away?

1:20:01.972 --> 1:20:03.400
Did she show
any signs of distress?

1:20:03.435 --> 1:20:06.370
She told her manager
and a lawyer.

1:20:08.407 --> 1:20:11.144
Harvey was aware that
there was a problem with Rose,

1:20:11.179 --> 1:20:13.608
but not that
she was accusing him of rape.

1:20:13.643 --> 1:20:16.182
So I draw a bright line
on the word "rape."

1:20:16.217 --> 1:20:18.580
Anything below that line,

1:20:18.615 --> 1:20:21.715
uh, he was aware of
feelings, concerns.

1:20:21.750 --> 1:20:23.156
Of what kind?

1:20:23.191 --> 1:20:24.454
I'm sorry. What...

1:20:24.489 --> 1:20:26.786
If the concerns
were not about rape,

1:20:26.821 --> 1:20:28.656
what were they about?

1:20:30.429 --> 1:20:33.463
The only way I can answer
is, um...

1:20:34.939 --> 1:20:36.466
...a sense of exploitation

1:20:36.501 --> 1:20:40.800
because of that
disparate power relationship.

1:20:40.835 --> 1:20:44.804
There's mental coercion
that isn't physical coercion.

1:20:44.839 --> 1:20:47.345
Lisa Bloom has been
working with Harvey

1:20:47.380 --> 1:20:49.050
to help him
recognize the difference.

1:20:49.085 --> 1:20:50.414
Lisa Bloom?

1:20:50.449 --> 1:20:52.251
Yeah.

1:20:52.286 --> 1:20:54.814
MEGAN:
If Harvey had been made aware

1:20:54.849 --> 1:21:00.061
of McGowan's concerns
at the time, how did he respond?

1:21:01.295 --> 1:21:03.592
I think he had dealings legally
with her about them.

1:21:03.627 --> 1:21:08.135
And how would you characterize
those legal dealings?

1:21:09.831 --> 1:21:11.402
I think he became aware that

1:21:11.437 --> 1:21:14.141
she did not regard
what happened as okay with her.

1:21:14.176 --> 1:21:15.703
I'm not talking about rape.

1:21:15.738 --> 1:21:19.949
I'm talking about the effect
he had on Rose McGowan.

1:21:19.984 --> 1:21:22.512
And that rather than fighting...

1:21:23.317 --> 1:21:24.954
"Rather than fighting"?

1:21:24.989 --> 1:21:28.188
Then... then what?

1:21:30.555 --> 1:21:33.721
I-I think he has agreed
to settlements

1:21:33.756 --> 1:21:36.394
rather than litigating
what might have been litigated.

1:21:36.429 --> 1:21:39.463
As Harvey saw it,
it was better to settle,

1:21:39.498 --> 1:21:41.267
even if you haven't done
anything wrong.

1:21:41.302 --> 1:21:43.533
He preferred to settle.

1:21:45.075 --> 1:21:48.604
Were there other cases of
questionable intimate relations

1:21:48.639 --> 1:21:51.244
with women
in which Weinstein settled?

1:21:53.512 --> 1:21:57.052
Let's say for now,
even on a background basis,

1:21:57.087 --> 1:21:59.681
that I need to find out
what my limits are legally.

1:21:59.716 --> 1:22:03.586
Even if on background,
I'm confirming settlements.

1:22:03.621 --> 1:22:08.228
But the-the answer is yes,
there have been.

1:22:10.925 --> 1:22:13.068
How many?

1:22:14.764 --> 1:22:16.302
(softly):
No.

1:22:17.074 --> 1:22:18.832
(Lanny chuckles)

1:22:18.867 --> 1:22:22.374
To admit to settlements this
early, they're in real trouble.

1:22:22.409 --> 1:22:24.178
-We need to find out a number.
-(Megan chuckles)

1:22:24.213 --> 1:22:25.641
We need to corroborate each one.

1:22:25.676 --> 1:22:27.643
-I'm on it.
-(phone vibrating)

1:22:27.678 --> 1:22:31.581
Have you guys had any dealings
with Diana Filip?

1:22:31.616 --> 1:22:33.715
-No. -I said no to speaking
at a women's conference.

1:22:33.750 --> 1:22:36.751
-She just keeps on calling me.
-Did you have her checked out?

1:22:36.786 --> 1:22:38.522
Security consultant says
she's legit,

1:22:38.557 --> 1:22:40.689
but who has time
for these random people?

1:22:42.891 --> 1:22:45.133
(phone vibrating)

1:22:54.034 --> 1:22:55.374
Hello?

1:22:55.409 --> 1:22:56.771
WOMAN (over phone):
I worked at Miramax.

1:22:56.806 --> 1:22:59.048
Talk to Irwin Reiter.
He hates Weinstein.

1:22:59.083 --> 1:23:00.478
(line clicks)

1:23:05.122 --> 1:23:07.353
(phone vibrating)

1:23:10.457 --> 1:23:12.259
Hey. Are you okay?

1:23:12.294 --> 1:23:15.064
JODI (over phone):
Did I wake you?

1:23:15.099 --> 1:23:17.627
Um, yeah. What's up?

1:23:17.662 --> 1:23:20.894
JODI: What do you know
about Irwin Reiter?

1:23:22.172 --> 1:23:25.305
Hang on.
I put together a file on him.

1:23:25.340 --> 1:23:28.539
I need to write
a good fucking email.

1:23:40.421 --> 1:23:43.158
Hi. Thanks for meeting me.

1:23:43.193 --> 1:23:44.918
You want to get me killed?

1:23:52.136 --> 1:23:56.765
So, Irwin, you've been an
accountant for the Weinsteins

1:23:56.800 --> 1:23:58.503
for 30 years.

1:24:00.067 --> 1:24:01.374
(pours drink)

1:24:01.409 --> 1:24:02.936
I pick up the check,

1:24:02.971 --> 1:24:04.872
and I reserve the right
to leave after five minutes.

1:24:04.907 --> 1:24:06.038
(clears throat)

1:24:06.073 --> 1:24:09.415
So, um...
what do you want to know?

1:24:09.450 --> 1:24:11.681
We have information
on several settlements

1:24:11.716 --> 1:24:13.485
that Weinstein made in the '90s,

1:24:13.520 --> 1:24:16.290
paid to actresses
and ex-employees.

1:24:16.325 --> 1:24:19.557
Could you tell me anything
about that?

1:24:21.627 --> 1:24:23.825
Could you confirm
those settlements

1:24:23.860 --> 1:24:25.431
and how it was
from your perspective?

1:24:25.466 --> 1:24:27.532
My perspective?

1:24:28.568 --> 1:24:30.931
Would it be company money
that was used?

1:24:32.506 --> 1:24:35.903
You wrote that we're from
the same tiny world.

1:24:35.938 --> 1:24:37.245
Yeah.

1:24:37.280 --> 1:24:39.313
Summers at bungalows
in the Catskills.

1:24:39.348 --> 1:24:41.942
Meals at Lefty's and Pop-Ins.

1:24:41.977 --> 1:24:44.945
What do you remember
about those holidays?

1:24:44.980 --> 1:24:48.256
Gosh, I remember so many things.

1:24:48.291 --> 1:24:49.983
It's the first time
I remember seeing

1:24:50.018 --> 1:24:52.084
my grandmother's arms bare.

1:24:52.119 --> 1:24:56.924
I knew those tattoos meant
something seismic.

1:24:56.959 --> 1:24:58.794
Yeah, h-how did you know?

1:24:58.829 --> 1:25:00.169
I just sensed it.

1:25:00.204 --> 1:25:03.238
Did your family discuss it?

1:25:06.408 --> 1:25:09.178
Who else are you talking to?

1:25:09.213 --> 1:25:11.510
I can't disclose that, Irwin.

1:25:13.679 --> 1:25:16.977
You know, my parents,
uh, they couldn't go there.

1:25:17.012 --> 1:25:19.386
They rarely discussed it.

1:25:20.653 --> 1:25:22.752
It's so mysterious, isn't it?

1:25:23.557 --> 1:25:25.920
Why some families talk.

1:25:25.955 --> 1:25:27.559
Some don't.

1:25:29.156 --> 1:25:34.159
The money Weinstein was
spending was, you know, crazy.

1:25:34.194 --> 1:25:35.204
I tried.

1:25:35.239 --> 1:25:36.898
I tried many times to

1:25:36.933 --> 1:25:39.868
get the board to do something
about him, but they just kept

1:25:39.903 --> 1:25:42.376
ignoring his behavior
and keeping him on.

1:25:42.411 --> 1:25:44.543
Why is that?

1:25:45.447 --> 1:25:48.349
Have you talked to L.O.C.?

1:25:48.384 --> 1:25:50.813
Or, uh, Z.P.?

1:25:50.848 --> 1:25:53.079
Who is L.O.C.?

1:25:53.114 --> 1:25:55.257
There was this memo.

1:25:55.292 --> 1:25:58.359
Let me ask you something, Jodi,
that's really puzzling me.

1:25:58.394 --> 1:26:01.087
Why are you asking
about the '90s

1:26:01.122 --> 1:26:04.860
when Weinstein has committed
so many more recent offenses?

1:26:06.270 --> 1:26:08.633
I got to go.

1:26:08.668 --> 1:26:10.932
-I'll give you a call.
-Irwin.

1:26:15.070 --> 1:26:17.312
♪ ♪

1:26:35.189 --> 1:26:38.432
(breathes deeply)

1:26:42.229 --> 1:26:44.031
(door opens)

1:26:44.066 --> 1:26:46.033
(crying):
Mom.

1:26:46.068 --> 1:26:47.672
I had a nightmare.

1:26:47.707 --> 1:26:50.807
-Oh, honey, come here.
-(sobs)

1:26:52.910 --> 1:26:56.417
-(crying softly)
-(shushing)

1:26:56.452 --> 1:26:58.683
(whispering):
It's okay. It's okay.

1:26:58.718 --> 1:27:00.487
I heard that
Ambra Battilana Gutierrez

1:27:00.522 --> 1:27:02.654
just got
a seven-figure settlement.

1:27:02.689 --> 1:27:06.625
And that Weinstein now owns
the audio of the incident?

1:27:07.892 --> 1:27:11.058
These settlements, Lanny...

1:27:11.093 --> 1:27:12.565
what are we talking?

1:27:13.799 --> 1:27:16.096
I can't tell you that, Megan.

1:27:16.131 --> 1:27:17.537
You know that.

1:27:17.572 --> 1:27:19.099
I'm not talking about
naming you, of course.

1:27:19.134 --> 1:27:22.905
It would just be great
for background

1:27:22.940 --> 1:27:24.170
to know a number

1:27:24.205 --> 1:27:27.074
of the other settlements
that you're aware of.

1:27:27.879 --> 1:27:30.242
-I'm not a bad guy here.
-I know that.

1:27:30.277 --> 1:27:32.651
My profession is
to get the facts

1:27:32.686 --> 1:27:35.489
into the hands
of reporters, but...

1:27:35.524 --> 1:27:38.393
(laughs):
you know, I can't help.

1:27:40.892 --> 1:27:43.860
I keep getting 40 in my head.

1:27:43.895 --> 1:27:44.960
(sighs)

1:27:44.995 --> 1:27:47.732
Which would be
ridiculous, right?

1:27:50.231 --> 1:27:51.967
Right?

1:27:52.002 --> 1:27:53.573
(smacks lips)

1:27:55.071 --> 1:27:56.477
It's not 40.

1:27:58.778 --> 1:28:02.582
Seriously, it's-it's,
uh, less than 40.

1:28:02.617 --> 1:28:04.584
Good. That's a relief.

1:28:04.619 --> 1:28:06.179
-(scoffs): Sure.
-(laughs)

1:28:08.117 --> 1:28:10.117
So...

1:28:10.922 --> 1:28:14.924
...less than half of 40, then?

1:28:14.959 --> 1:28:15.859
Check.

1:28:15.894 --> 1:28:17.366
Oh, and what the fuck, Lanny?

1:28:17.401 --> 1:28:19.962
We heard that Ronan Farrow
is working on a story.

1:28:19.997 --> 1:28:21.029
No, no.

1:28:21.064 --> 1:28:23.867
That is done. Over.

1:28:25.475 --> 1:28:28.036
I don't see you
as a bad guy, Lanny.

1:28:28.841 --> 1:28:31.413
I-I don't. I never have.
I respect you.

1:28:31.448 --> 1:28:33.041
Uh, I respect you.

1:28:35.881 --> 1:28:37.947
(sighs)

1:28:37.982 --> 1:28:41.181
This is all
gonna come out, Lanny.

1:28:41.216 --> 1:28:43.183
Publicly.

1:28:43.218 --> 1:28:44.558
Generally does.

1:28:44.593 --> 1:28:46.659
(chuckles)

1:28:46.694 --> 1:28:48.826
-(laughs): Okay.
-(laughing)

1:28:50.632 --> 1:28:53.435
Wh... What am I laughing about?

1:28:53.470 --> 1:28:55.327
(both laugh)

1:28:55.362 --> 1:28:58.671
(sighs):
Oh, Megan.

1:28:59.608 --> 1:29:01.003
Lanny.

1:29:09.651 --> 1:29:11.882
I'd say eight to 12 settlements.

1:29:17.461 --> 1:29:19.494
(sighs softly)

1:29:24.765 --> 1:29:27.667
And do you think that's normal?

1:29:27.702 --> 1:29:29.834
For men to make so many payoffs?

1:29:35.138 --> 1:29:37.908
I do. Yeah.

1:29:41.408 --> 1:29:43.980
It feels like we're so close.

1:29:44.015 --> 1:29:47.951
Do you think we'll get it?
What if we don't?

1:29:47.986 --> 1:29:49.689
I'm having nightmares about him.

1:29:49.724 --> 1:29:52.560
-Oh, my God. I have them, too.
-Yeah?

1:29:52.595 --> 1:29:54.353
I'm terrified we know all this

1:29:54.388 --> 1:29:57.796
and we might go to our graves
knowing it.

1:29:57.831 --> 1:29:59.391
The story will run.

1:29:59.426 --> 1:30:02.900
My worry is people won't care.

1:30:02.935 --> 1:30:06.134
And he won't even be
slowed down, let alone stopped.

1:30:06.169 --> 1:30:08.609
It's like
an ocean of wrongdoing.

1:30:08.644 --> 1:30:10.105
I mean, can you imagine

1:30:10.140 --> 1:30:13.548
how many Harveys there are
out there, every day?

1:30:13.583 --> 1:30:15.814
I sometimes wonder...

1:30:18.445 --> 1:30:22.150
...when I had Mira, if...

1:30:23.351 --> 1:30:27.254
...if all the trauma,
not just in me but in...

1:30:27.289 --> 1:30:30.796
but in all w-women I talked to,
if it just...

1:30:30.831 --> 1:30:33.062
this darkness,
this constant violence,

1:30:33.097 --> 1:30:35.801
if it just sort of imploded.

1:30:36.738 --> 1:30:41.576
Maybe-maybe that's part of
the depression that hits women.

1:30:45.142 --> 1:30:48.275
Do you wish you hadn't
signed up for this story?

1:30:50.081 --> 1:30:51.883
Do you?

1:30:53.381 --> 1:30:54.446
No.

1:30:54.481 --> 1:30:56.756
(chuckles):
No.

1:31:03.127 --> 1:31:07.734
JODI: The last time we met,
you mentioned a memo?

1:31:13.709 --> 1:31:14.939
(smacks lips)

1:31:14.974 --> 1:31:18.613
It was, uh,
from an ex-executive,

1:31:18.648 --> 1:31:20.439
and it was extensive, scathing.

1:31:20.474 --> 1:31:21.979
She sent it to the board.

1:31:22.014 --> 1:31:24.344
When was this?
How did they react?

1:31:24.379 --> 1:31:26.445
Oh, it was a short burst
of behind-doors mayhem,

1:31:26.480 --> 1:31:28.480
and then she left.

1:31:28.515 --> 1:31:30.889
What did her memo say?

1:31:30.924 --> 1:31:33.221
That the company was
a toxic environment.

1:31:35.522 --> 1:31:37.192
Would anyone have a copy?

1:31:37.227 --> 1:31:38.864
(laughs)

1:31:44.234 --> 1:31:45.805
Hey.

1:31:46.940 --> 1:31:49.776
-Sorry it's so late.
-Mm.

1:31:52.308 --> 1:31:54.473
-(Megan sighs)
-JODI:<i> You okay?</i>

1:31:54.508 --> 1:31:56.585
Uh, Talia was up late.

1:31:56.620 --> 1:31:58.048
Violet woke up twice.

1:31:58.083 --> 1:32:00.413
I have an inbox
filled with enraged people

1:32:00.448 --> 1:32:03.823
about this insurance story,
which is going to be huge.

1:32:03.858 --> 1:32:07.486
There's already
hundreds of emails here,

1:32:07.521 --> 1:32:08.861
and there is... (laughs)

1:32:08.896 --> 1:32:11.127
a hurricane
heading towards Florida.

1:32:11.162 --> 1:32:13.492
So, I am going to somehow
fly down there

1:32:13.527 --> 1:32:15.098
and move my dad someplace else

1:32:15.133 --> 1:32:17.166
before he is
literally blown away.

1:32:17.201 --> 1:32:20.532
And I have a slight
nervous twitch in my eye.

1:32:20.567 --> 1:32:22.270
Let me see.

1:32:24.879 --> 1:32:26.571
(Ron sighs)

1:32:26.606 --> 1:32:29.343
(laughter, playful chatter)

1:32:30.786 --> 1:32:32.445
-Hey. Hey.
-Come here, Crabby.

1:32:32.480 --> 1:32:34.689
-Get that raisin. -Holly?
-(laughter continues)

1:32:34.724 --> 1:32:36.482
-(ringtone playing)
-Slow down!

1:32:36.517 --> 1:32:38.891
Um, here. Will you hold
Crabby for a second?

1:32:38.926 --> 1:32:40.321
Least they're having fun.

1:32:41.555 --> 1:32:43.192
Hi. This is Jodi Kantor.

1:32:43.227 --> 1:32:44.897
ROWENA (over phone):
This is Rowena Chiu.

1:32:44.932 --> 1:32:46.734
I'm in New York.

1:32:46.769 --> 1:32:48.901
Do you still want to meet up?

1:32:49.739 --> 1:32:51.838
ROWENA:
I couldn't tell anyone.

1:32:51.873 --> 1:32:55.204
Not my parents,
not even my husband.

1:32:55.239 --> 1:32:56.975
Why not?

1:32:58.077 --> 1:33:00.407
I grew up
in an immigrant household.

1:33:00.442 --> 1:33:03.146
I was taught
to keep my head down,

1:33:03.181 --> 1:33:07.018
work hard and not draw
attention to myself, you know?

1:33:07.053 --> 1:33:08.514
In Chinese culture,

1:33:08.549 --> 1:33:12.452
I felt I had to protect
my family at all costs.

1:33:12.487 --> 1:33:15.994
And I was young, scared.

1:33:18.361 --> 1:33:21.802
Can you tell me anything about
what happened in Venice?

1:33:24.070 --> 1:33:27.005
This is off the record, yeah?

1:33:30.670 --> 1:33:32.208
I had the evening shifts,

1:33:32.243 --> 1:33:35.343
going through notes
on screenplays with Harvey.

1:33:35.378 --> 1:33:41.217
One night, we were working,
and he kept trying to touch me.

1:33:41.252 --> 1:33:43.417
I didn't want to make him angry.

1:33:43.452 --> 1:33:46.860
He's a very big man.

1:33:46.895 --> 1:33:49.159
I kept trying
to get back to the notes.

1:33:49.194 --> 1:33:52.492
And that went on
for a few hours,

1:33:52.527 --> 1:33:54.461
just trying to avoid him.

1:33:54.496 --> 1:33:56.529
How did you do that?

1:33:57.741 --> 1:34:00.533
I would just fight him off.

1:34:01.701 --> 1:34:03.503
I'd worn two pairs of tights

1:34:03.538 --> 1:34:07.672
to buy me some time
if I ever needed it.

1:34:07.707 --> 1:34:10.510
But finally,

1:34:10.545 --> 1:34:13.854
he held me down.

1:34:13.889 --> 1:34:17.858
Not forcefully,
but like it was a game.

1:34:17.893 --> 1:34:19.024
(stammers softly)

1:34:19.059 --> 1:34:23.391
Then he parted my legs,

1:34:23.426 --> 1:34:25.327
and he said...

1:34:26.462 --> 1:34:30.871
"Please, just one thrust,
and it'll all be over."

1:34:34.811 --> 1:34:36.041
I got away.

1:34:36.076 --> 1:34:38.010
I was traumatized.

1:34:38.045 --> 1:34:39.308
I was a Christian.

1:34:39.343 --> 1:34:42.113
I was still
with my first boyfriend.

1:34:42.148 --> 1:34:44.610
And you shared this with Zelda?

1:34:44.645 --> 1:34:50.055
